RStoolbox 0.0.0.9000
=====================================
* new function ggRGB as an raster::plotRGB equivalent for ggplot2

* new functions `readSLI` and `writeSLI` to read and write binary ENVI spectral libraries

* new family of functions for Landsat processing: 
	`readMeta()` reads Landsat Metadata from MTL files
   	`stackLS()` loads all Landsat bands into a raster stack in one go based on MTL metadata
   	`radCor()` performs radiometric calibration and correction for LS5 TM, LS7 TM and LS8 TM

* new function `superClass()` for random forest based supervised classification 